<p>the Intelligence and Security Agency, arts. 5&#8211;6; Brazil (footnote 2), art. 4; Canada, Security 
Intelligence Service Act, sects. 12&#8211;16; Australia (footnote 3), sect. 17. This practice was also 
recommended in Morocco, Instance equit&#233; et r&#233;conciliation, rapport final, Vol. I, V&#233;rit&#233;, equit&#233; et 
