</p>
<p>Operational Activities, art. 23(2)1&#8211;2; Croatia (footnote 2), art. 112; Norway (footnote 22), sect. 2. In 
South Africa, the Inspector-General for intelligence examines intelligence services&#8217; compliance with 
the law and Constitution; see South Africa, Intelligence Services Oversight Act, sect. 7(7) a-b. 
</p>
