</p>
<p>117
  A/HRC/13/37, paras. 11&#8211;13. For specific examples of international principles, see the Council of 
</p>
<p>Europe Convention for the Protection of Individuals with regard to Automatic Processing of Personal 
Data (No. 108); the Organization for Economic Cooperation and Development, Guidelines on the 
Protection of Privacy and Transborder Data Flows of Personal Data (1980); The Guidelines for the 
