  Sweden (footnote 27), art. 3; Switzerland (footnote 5), art. 18 (1). 
</p>
<p> 
</p>
<p>136
  David Banisar, Public oversight and national security: Comparative approaches to freedom of 
</p>
<p>information, Marina Caparini and Hans Born (eds.), Democratic control of intelligence services: 
Containing the rogue elephant, p. 217. 
</p>
